# Get all properties for a tenant
# Description: Returns all properties for the tenant. Tenant id may be provided via `X-Tenant-ID` header or `?tenantId=` query.

# Alternative using header
### Get all properties (header)
GET http://localhost:3097/tenant/property
X-Tenant-ID: d2c5b2f0-f5c7-11f0-937d-1a220d8ac2c9
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJ..._Q5o
